                Contents^^Publisher's Preface^1. The Evangelist and His Message^2. Evangelistic Messages^3. Great Gospel Texts^4. Vital Soul-searching Questions^5. Familiar Gospel Texts^6. Salvation Truths^7. Truths for the Anxious^8. Gospel Blessings^9. Messages of Warning^10. Remarkable Conversions^11. Truths for New Converts^12. Themes for Special Occasions^Index page 123
                - Publisher
            
                "Preach the Word" was the admonition that Paul gave to the young preacher, Timothy. What was so essential 2000 years ago is still necessary today. To "preach the Word" is to expound the Scripture truths with clarity and conviction. The John Ritchie Sermon Ouline Series brings out truths that change lives and minister to present needs. These aids are not intended to diminish a personal, prayerful study of the Bible. Rather, they will encourage it by offering inspiring insights to those who preach or teach God's truths. The busy preacher or lay person will find helpful and stimulating ideas for a dynamic preaching or teaching ministry in these sermon outlines.
                - Publisher
            
                Born out of an evangelistic zeal, these books include material from a great variety of sources gathered throughout a ministry lasting forty years.
                - Publisher


